{"tid":371920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廿三條] 睇到澳門咁，諗起一樣嘢","createTime":"2017-08-24T03:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T03:46:46.000Z","uid":23170,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d628d1d9025c968f46091014dbc1b3cebb20810","tid":371920,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"任何戰爭都應該未雨稠謀，林鄭講到明佢會再有意推返廿三條，澳門正正就係一個抗爭嘅借鏡，遊行但係政府廢中廢老無理過，照通過左，香港唔可以成為第二同最後嘅失敗例子。依家諗定將來要點抗爭差唔多。"},{"pid":"570148f6241636ccdd8ad4ac67a8df81e866bfa1","tid":371920,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"澳門做錯過嘅，香港人唔好再重踏。今日見到嘅澳門，如果我地乜都唔做，我地就係下一個。"},{"pid":"f240e56b1c82e043e00cb467f4f3ccb1bef90cc7","tid":371920,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:45:25.000Z","msg":"岩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbce962fb77b7a8e5fda08175554d83d3501934","tid":371920,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb7595361cd783cf72a7b63d5c48531398cfd18","tid":371920,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"岩，唔好俾香港變成另一個澳門。抵抗支共，人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}